beer.beer_description:
The beer made in collaboration with Shane Warne.

99 Not Out SKW Pale Ale is a sessionable, new world style Pale Ale.  Hopped with New Zealand Kohatu and Cascade hops, it displays spicy/earthy hop notes, a strong malt backbone and a nicely balanced bitterness (35 IBUs). SKW Pale Ale is the perfect beer for summer.
